data.description: Nestled in the heart of Great Falls, this secluded sanctuary on a corner lot offers a welcoming place of comfort in a charming and lively neighborhood. Located just down the street from Great Falls High School, at almost 2,200 sq.', this 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home has open living spaces on both levels, floor to ceiling windows showering the space with natural light, and an oversized garage with added workshop space. Don’t miss your opportunity to own a well-maintained home in a pleasant and desirable neighborhood. Listed by Polly Pearson & Abby Williams.
